{
  "stem": "17867.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 159.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then the last one that we finally went to said to us that yes, she had seen her.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And by this time, she had given up all hope of us being alive and she said, if they killed them, [SOBBING] I don't want to live.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "She gave herself up and they killed her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] That was the end of my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[SOBBING] So it just left my mother and I.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] That's what we were hoping for.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she wouldn't stay because she kept searching for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She would go from one farm to another farm, the ones, the people that we knew that she thought for sure we would be there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she just kept going and going and going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we kept following her, but could never catch up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said that they said they would keep her for a little bit, but she says, no, I have to look for my mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then like I said, she gave up all hope of finding us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She thought they got us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She figured, my mother running with a small child, they must have gotten us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she just said, I can't live like this, I cannot be the only one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was my oldest sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she must have been [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] maybe 15.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She must have been about that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm just guessing, I was really too young to remember all the ages and dates or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, constant running-- running and hiding and hiding and running.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came to a cemetery place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to hide there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother prayed for rain so we could have something to drink.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
